N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4815.1 - License required

State Regulations

No person, firm or corporation shall sell or distribute
bingo supplies or equipment to any authorized organization licensed to conduct
bingo without having first obtained a license therefor as provided in the Bingo

Control Law and this Chapter. Notes
